{"tid":646480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德美促中共放劉霞出國","createTime":"2018-04-29T05:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T05:41:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"acafd112b06924d7ef685fb2df12cc9ca5d76f91","tid":646480,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:33:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180428/20375367?_ga=2.112248452.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180428%2F20375367%3F_ga%3D2.112248452.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=RmHe%2F8bsTW7GfwpB%2FNHOFttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ec4cd61c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180428%2F20375367%3F_ga%3D2.112248452.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=71d2385c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180428/20375367?_ga=2.112248452.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月28日 <br />\n<br />\n德美促中共放劉霞出國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180428/large/lau01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180428%2Flarge%2Flau01.jpg&h=e6804086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波去年7月病逝後，其遺孀劉霞（圖）一直被當局軟禁。據中資背景英文《南華早報》披露，德國和美國再次呼籲，要求中共當局釋放劉霞並允她出國。報道另引消息稱，此事件遠超出中共外交或公安部控制範圍，而由更高層官員處理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n超出外交部或公安部控制<br />\n<br />\n德國駐華大使柯慕賢（Michael Clauss）接受該報記者訪問表示，希望劉霞能獲迅速而積極的結果，「我們希望劉霞能夠行動自由，並能隨心所欲地旅行。這是德國長期關注的問題，如果她希望前來，德國會歡迎她。」美駐華大使館發言人在一份聲明中也表示，華盛頓對劉霞深表關切，「美國繼續呼籲中國當局取消對劉霞行動及通訊上的限制，在她願意情況下允許她離開中國」。報道引消息稱，劉霞一案遠超出外交部或公安部的控制範圍，「實際上是由更高層負責」。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部過往在記者會上多次被問到劉霞去向。去年12月劉曉波生忌當日，外交部發言人華春瑩被問到劉霞能否出國時稱，劉霞是自由的；惟有關說法未獲證實。另一名發言人陸慷也稱，劉霞是中國國民，依法享有一切自由。路透社日前引知情人士透露，中共當局一直延遲與西方政府商討讓劉霞出國事宜。報道又引述有份參與游說工作的外交人員表示，對劉霞能夠在短期內獲釋出國不感樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/德國之聲中文網  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n莫迪訪華　一日六度晤習<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\nIT業新福利招攬人才　開創另類奇職　 美女「鼓勵師」　為程式員減壓"},{"pid":"2b48c60f02b5f200856df0826014eb1eb28683d3","tid":646480,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:34:53.000Z","msg":"厲害了"},{"pid":"48ed36aa05b423007418fb20eb0888cc54f32974","tid":646480,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:36:19.000Z","msg":"一個超級大倒退既國家，會放既機率比鄧肛胡時期更低"},{"pid":"844a1c2afb8674496534312fde6c0270a71afee7","tid":646480,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:37:42.000Z","msg":"洗頭艇"},{"pid":"d9637214589bf10073c77c113915b7d04a4268bf","tid":646480,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a35287b5654374b5033c7a4dde57ef5d333b683","tid":646480,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"五毛#99568Me係鬼仔大頭相<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/123409_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F123409_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=6280b844&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22f96f2e9970bc6a2799377a9e5c35f3d0374313","tid":646480,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9637214589bf10073c77c113915b7d04a4268bf","tid":646480,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:41:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛戚繼光<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/134155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F134155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e46b5def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"}]}